You are a traitor...

617
01:12:25,501 --> 01:12:29,087
you are a collaborator,
and you are a counterrevolutionary!

618
01:12:35,845 --> 01:12:38,555
Did you write this?

619
01:12:38,639 --> 01:12:40,557
And you call it a confession?

620
01:12:40,641 --> 01:12:44,603
