A child's fairy tale.

621
01:12:56,157 --> 01:12:58,825
- What do you want me to confess?
- You know what you did...

622
01:12:58,910 --> 01:13:00,827
and what others did.

623
01:13:00,912 --> 01:13:03,121
So why don't you volunteer
the information?

624
01:13:03,206 --> 01:13:04,873
I do not understand.

625
01:13:04,957 --> 01:13:07,876
