724
01:25:25,614 --> 01:25:27,949
They will give you asylum there

725
01:25:29,034 --> 01:25:31,661
I'm sure they will.

726
01:25:31,745 --> 01:25:36,207
Chang, take my car to the south gate.
I want you to drive His Majesty.

727
01:26:33,724 --> 01:26:36,642
[ Officer Shouts ]

728
01:26:36,727 --> 01:26:38,978
Your Majesty!

729
01:26:47,112 --> 01:26:50,323
[ Soldiers Shouting, Cheering ]

730
01:26:58,624 --> 01:27:00,791
[ Shouting, Cheering Continue ]

731
01:27:26,526 --> 01:27:28,778
- Please, Your Majesty.
