763
01:29:59,429 --> 01:30:03,224
most ofChina came under the control
ofGeneral Chiang Kai-shek —

764
01:30:03,308 --> 01:30:05,559
the so-called nationalists...

765
01:30:05,644 --> 01:30:07,728
the Kuomintang.

766
01:30:07,813 --> 01:30:10,981
- What were your relations with them?
